♪ Blossom,
commander and the leader ♪

22:52.015 --> 22:55.005
♪ Bubbles, she has the joy
and the laughter ♪

22:55.007 --> 22:58.001
♪ Buttercup,
she's the toughest fighter ♪

22:58.003 --> 23:00.019
♪ Powerpuffs save the day ♪

23:00.021 --> 23:05.006
♪ Fighting crime,
trying to save the world ♪

23:05.008 --> 23:08.018
♪ Here they come, just in time ♪

23:08.020 --> 23:11.018
